00:01:34.180 --> 00:01:36.080
get 3 wins in a row.

00:01:36.080 --> 00:01:36.340
OK.

00:01:36.340 --> 00:01:38.970
So this is the odds of winning
the coin toss,

00:01:38.970 --> 00:01:39.990
not the game, no.

00:01:39.990 --> 00:01:41.670
I could see Brady doing this.

00:01:41.670 --> 00:01:42.990
I thought he was giving
